## What happened

Flutter app was normally working, when app uninstalled from the android
device and try to install using Run/main.dart.
Not installing app on the android device.

(please describe what you were doing when this exception occurred)

Tools • Dart 2.12.0 (build 2.12.0-29.10.beta)
